        "content_1": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "About This Product",
            "heading": "Why UAE Parents Choose the U-Shaped Toothbrush",
            "subheading": "Designed for little mouths, loved by busy families",
            "body": "<p>The Kids U-Shaped Electric Toothbrush revolutionises oral care for children aged 2 to 12 across the UAE. Its innovative 360-degree silicone head wraps around every tooth simultaneously, delivering a thorough clean in just 60 seconds — turning brushing from a daily struggle into a moment kids look forward to.</p><p>Food-grade silicone bristles are softer than traditional nylon, protecting developing gums while removing plaque effectively. The IPX7 waterproof rating means worry-free use in the bath or shower, and the rechargeable battery lasts up to 60 days on a single charge — ideal for travel between Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and beyond.</p><p>Parents in the UAE trust this toothbrush because it works with how kids actually brush, not against it. The ergonomic handle fits small hands, the gentle vibration frequency is calibrated for children, and the one-button operation means even toddlers can start learning independence. Pair it with our Strawberry Foam Toothpaste for a complete oral care routine delivered free across the Emirates with Cash on Delivery available.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_2": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "",
            "heading": "Food-Grade Silicone — Safe for Kids",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>Every bristle on the U-shaped head is made from FDA-approved food-grade silicone — the same material used in baby bottle teats and pacifiers. It is completely BPA-free and non-toxic, giving parents total peace of mind. The soft silicone flexes to follow the natural curve of each tooth, making brushing comfortable even for toddlers with sensitive gums.</p><p>The brush handle is ergonomically sized for small hands, and the one-button operation means kids as young as two can start building independent brushing habits. A built-in 60-second auto-timer ensures the right brushing duration every single time.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_3": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "",
            "heading": "Complete Kids Dental Care Set",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>Pair the U-shaped toothbrush with our <strong>Kids Strawberry Foam Toothpaste</strong> for the ultimate brushing experience — the foam fills every gap in the U-shape for maximum coverage. Need replacement heads? Our <strong>Kids Silicone U Brush Heads</strong> snap on in seconds, and dentists recommend changing them every three months. Save even more with the <strong>Kids Dental Care Bundle</strong> that includes everything your child needs for a complete oral care routine.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
        "content_4": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "",
            "heading": "Free Next-Day Delivery Across the UAE",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>Order your kids U-shaped electric toothbrush before 8 PM and receive <strong>free next-day delivery</strong> anywhere in the UAE — Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, RAK, Fujairah, and Umm Al Quwain. Cash on delivery is available on every order. Not happy? Return it within 14 days for a full refund.</p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
